{"tid":2169385,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"都2，3年啦 有人知山神幾多週薪未？","createTime":"2020-08-22T12:47:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T19:53:43.000Z","uid":42246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e33994c7cfba2df368aec660a31a210984cd4700","tid":2169385,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T12:47:25.000Z","msg":"會唔會成為球壇不解之迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國際米蘭周四(6日)官方宣布，今季由曼聯外借助陣嘅智利前鋒阿歷斯山齊士，以自由身免轉會費正式加盟，簽約3年至2023年6月，年薪據報道為700萬歐元(約6400萬港元)，比在曼聯領取薪支大幅削減74%。<br />\n今次交易可謂大團圓結局，曼聯終於卸下每周50萬鎊薪金嘅沉重負擔，英國傳媒報道，山齊士加盟國米，周薪折實約只有13萬鎊，人工大減74%。<br />\n不過山齊士在國米陣中獲得重用，可以一展所長，似番個球星，而國米又可免轉會費獲得山齊士，實為3贏結局。<br />\n<span class=\"red\">有傳媒為曼聯總結今次簽入這位「鋼琴球星」嘅損失，山齊士喺曼聯支全薪共79星期，每周50.5萬鎊，外借國米49星期，每周39.5萬鎊，總計曼聯為佢支出5930萬鎊(約6億港元)，佢為曼聯射入5球，每球價值1190萬鎊，貴絕足球史，依家佢轉投國米，曼聯終於脫苦海</span>囉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://On.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FOn.cc&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6ZFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=8546fe46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">On.cc</a>"},{"pid":"58441edf9e6cff949c6fb5145af6d0cfa2412b84","tid":2169385,"uid":42246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T12:48:31.000Z","msg":"班仆街吹吹下吹到50.5週薪<br />\n個0.5係通脹？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e345ee6311f098706e0c52b47eccc98a9cc756","tid":2169385,"uid":111460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T12:48:37.000Z","msg":"仲有人信山神收錢踢波"},{"pid":"790629c274933b467558176af56f180981fd